         <abstract id="aspace_0720cfdecce4b5b9d6391edc185c33ac">Research material including data on poison gas collected during World War I by the Chemical Warfare Services and for his book: The Lethal War Gases (1919). Included also are experimental data on food and diet and correspondence relating to his teaching career at Yale University as well as on his publications.</abstract>
